name: Big Boomers!
Lore: 'Gungan weaponry can be quite sophisticated. Sometimes its users are not.',
Text: 'If there is more than 1 card in opponent''s Force Pile, opponent must use 1 Force. OR Take a Fambaa or Booma into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR If you just drew weapon destiny for your Booma, cancel that destiny to cause a re-draw.',
